<li id="cite_note-Neither_White_Nor_Black-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Neither_White_Nor_Black_8-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Neither_White_Nor_Black_8-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Neither_White_Nor_Black_8-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Neither_White_Nor_Black_8-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Neither_White_Nor_Black_8-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Neither_White_Nor_Black_8-5"><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Neither_White_Nor_Black_8-6"><sup><i><b>g</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBushMauss1984" class="citation book cs1">Bush, Lester E. Jr.; <a href="/wiki/Armand_L._Mauss" class="mw-redirect" title="Armand L. Mauss">Mauss, Armand L.</a>, eds. (1984). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20221001163611/http://signaturebookslibrary.org/neither-white-nor-black/"><i>Neither White Nor Black: Mormon Scholars Confront the Race Issue in a Universal Church</i></a>. Salt Lake City, Utah: <a href="/wiki/Signature_Books" title="Signature Books">Signature Books</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-941214-22-2" title="Special:BookSources/0-941214-22-2"><bdi>0-941214-22-2</bdi></a>. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://signaturebookslibrary.org/neither-white-nor-black/">the original</a> on October 1, 2022 &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Internet_Archive" title="Internet Archive">Internet Archive</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Neither+White+Nor+Black%3A+Mormon+Scholars+Confront+the+Race+Issue+in+a+Universal+Church&amp;rft.place=Salt+Lake+City%2C+Utah&