<li id="cite_note-42"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-42">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Bible_(King_James)/Genesis#28:1" class="extiw" title="s:Bible (King James)/Genesis">Genesis 28:1</a></span>
