<li id="cite_note-51"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-51">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFSmith1948" class="citation book cs1">Smith, George (1948). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://byustudies.byu.edu/content/volume-5-chapter-12"><i>History of the Church, Vol. 5</i></a>. Salt Lake City: <a href="/wiki/Deseret_Book" class="mw-redirect" title="Deseret Book">Deseret Book</a>. p.&#160;217 &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/BYU" class="mw-redirect" title="BYU">BYU</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=History+of+the+Church%2C+Vol.+5&amp;rft.place=Salt+Lake+City&amp;rft.pages=217&amp;rft.pub=Deseret+Book&amp;rft.date=1948&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=George&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbyustudies.byu.edu%2Fcontent%2Fvolume-5-chapter-12&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AInterracial+marriage+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
