</li>
<li id="cite_note-69"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-69">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFQuinn1997" class="citation book cs1"><a href="/wiki/D._Michael_Quinn" title="D. Michael Quinn">Quinn, D. Michael</a> (1997). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=VnbZAAAAMAAJ"><i>The Mormon Hierarchy: Extensions of Power</i></a>. <a href="/wiki/Signature_Books" title="Signature Books">Signature Books</a>. p.&#160;256. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781560850601" title="Special:BookSources/9781560850601"><bdi>9781560850601</bdi></a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Google_Books" title="Google Books">Google Books</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Mormon+Hierarchy%3A+Extensions+of+Power&amp;rft.pages=256&amp;rft.pub=Signature+Books&amp;rft.date=1997&amp;rft.isbn=9781560850601&amp;rft.aulast=Quinn&amp;rft.aufirst=D.+Michael&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DVnbZAAAAMAAJ&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AInterracial+marriage+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
