<li id="cite_note-80"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-80">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFWhalen1964" class="citation book cs1">Whalen, William Joseph (1964). <span class="id-lock-limited" title="Free access subject to limited trial, subscription normally required"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=O4TZAAAAMAAJ"><i>The Latter-Day Saints in the Modern Day World: An Account of Contemporary Mormonism</i></a></span>. New York City: <a href="/wiki/John_Day_Company" title="John Day Company">John Day Company</a>. p.&#160;254<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">September 16,</span> 2017</span> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Google_Books" title="Google Books">Google Books</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Latter-Day+Saints+in+the+Modern+Day+World%3A+An+Account+of+Contemporary+Mormonism&amp;rft.place=New+York+City&amp;rft.pages=254&amp;rft.pub=John+Day+Company&amp;rft.date=1964&amp;rft.aulast=Whalen&amp;rft.aufirst=William+Joseph&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DO4TZAAAAMAAJ&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AInterracial+marriage+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
