<li id="cite_note-84"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-84">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFMontgomery2012" class="citation news cs1">Montgomery, Morton (October 31, 2012). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.dailykos.com/stories/2012/10/31/1153215/-George-W-Romney-s-Franken-Son-Mitt-His-Noble-Lies">"George W. Romney's Franken-Son: Mitt &amp; His 'Noble' Lies"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/The_Daily_Kos" class="mw-redirect" title="The Daily Kos">The Daily Kos</a></i>. Kos Media<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">August 28,</span> 2017</span>. <q>I fully agree the Negro is entitled to considerations, also stated above, but not full social benefits nor inter-marriage privileges with the Whites, nor should the Whites be forced to accept them into restricted White areas.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Daily+Kos&amp;rft.atitle=George+W.+Romney%27s+Franken-Son%3A+Mitt+%26+His+%27Noble%27+Lies&amp;rft.date=2012-10-31&amp;rft.aulast=Montgomery&amp;rft.aufirst=Morton&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailykos.com%2Fstories%2F2012%2F10%2F31%2F1153215%2F-George-W-Romney-s-Franken-Son-Mitt-His-Noble-Lies&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AInterracial+marriage+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-BYU-85"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-BYU_85-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BYU_85-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBergera2013" class="citation journal cs1">Bergera, Gary James (Summer 2013). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://issuu.com/utah10/docs/uhq_volume81_2013_number3/s/10418366">"<span class="cs1-kern-left"></span>'This Time of Crisis': The Race-Based Anti-BYU Athletic Protests of 1968–1971"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Utah_Historical_Quarterly" title="Utah Historical Quarterly">Utah Historical Quarterly</a></i>. <b>81</b> (3): 204–229. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F45063320">10.2307/45063320</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/45063320">45063320</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:254446844">254446844</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Utah+Historical+Quarterly&amp;rft.atitle=%27This+Time+of+Crisis%27%3A+The+Race-Based+Anti-BYU+Athletic+Protests+of+1968%E2%80%931971&amp;rft.ssn=summer&amp;rft.volume=81&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=204-229&amp;rft.date=2013&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A254446844%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F45063320%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F45063320&amp;rft.aulast=Bergera&amp;rft.aufirst=Gary+James&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%