</li>
<li id="cite_note-Dates-86"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Dates_86-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Dates_86-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation news cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/local/1978/07/15/mormons-oppose-dates-marriage-to-interracial/33b0330d-8954-4669-9969-671d77d35659/">"Mormons Oppose Dates, Marriage To Interracial"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/The_Washington_Post" title="The Washington Post">The Washington Post</a></i>. July 15, 1978<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">August 26,</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Washington+Post&amp;rft.atitle=Mormons+Oppose+Dates%2C+Marriage+To+Interracial&amp;rft.date=1978-07-15&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Farchive%2Flocal%2F1978%2F07%2F15%2Fmormons-oppose-dates-marriage-to-interracial%2F33b0330d-8954-4669-9969-671d77d35659%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AInterracial+marriage+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
